Adams/Clay vs Jacksonian

"meae.congressional.congress18.la.county" %>% 
  get_county_map_data() %>% 
  filter(!is.na(state_abbr),
         cross_ref != "New to dataset") %>%
  arrange(!is.na(federalist_percentage), !is.na(demrep_percentage), 
          cnty_type == "Parish") %>% 
  map_counties()
